{"tid":1958614,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[台仔企硬]可能係第一個因為唔跪支那而熄ser既game","createTime":"2020-04-04T19:09:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T12:10:12.000Z","uid":28013,"like":86,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"fe616e5b398220b18dfb2563d9f99d8bef21a4a1","tid":1958614,"uid":28013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T19:09:20.000Z","msg":"事緣大陸有隻武俠game叫劍俠情緣三由<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">西山居</span></span>代理，係台灣都有代理台服（由網銀國際代理）<br />\n４月４號因為支那個邊全國哀悼李文亮同抗疫死左既人就停晒遊戲娛樂之類既野<br />\n台服都收到order，象徵式臨時維護三個鐘停服<br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/202004/b6127bde659a50f714d347be5376a426.JPG?w=1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F202004%2Fb6127bde659a50f714d347be5376a426.JPG%3Fw%3D1000&h=889c2eb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後就有唔乖乖地哀悼既大陸仔偷渡去台服見到有人講中國武漢肺炎就嬲嬲豬掉左上劍三既百度貼吧（類似支那版既巴哈咁）<br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/202004/c502274f66ba875371757a8fd019547e.JPG?w=1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F202004%2Fc502274f66ba875371757a8fd019547e.JPG%3Fw%3D1000&h=aa4f162a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後原廠見到<br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/202004/d73fa3bd2281c406b4cc1ec857a8d323.JPG?w=1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F202004%2Fd73fa3bd2281c406b4cc1ec857a8d323.JPG%3Fw%3D1000&h=a3231245&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n於是第一個比人周到既玩家<span style=\"color: red;\">黑馬戰光</span>就比台服ＢＡＮ左<br />\n之後台服既玩家唔順氣，紛紛係對話頻道到刷頻，越黎越多人比官方禁言同ＢＡＮ<br />\n<blockquote>2020年4月4日晚上11點40分<br />\n台服劍三全體頻道全體玩家實施禁言<br />\n全體頻道包含密語世界陣營好友幫會通通無法說話<br />\n同時被官方封鎖帳號的人數正在不停上升。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/202004/708a387af730ae7d0249d8713e60a077.JPG?w=1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F202004%2F708a387af730ae7d0249d8713e60a077.JPG%3Fw%3D1000&h=7c0d2440&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/202004/cb51e537cc4d9fcbe1d8d93fd2b0d1e4.JPG?w=1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F202004%2Fcb51e537cc4d9fcbe1d8d93fd2b0d1e4.JPG%3Fw%3D1000&h=67fbc539&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPS: 圖入面唯一講緊野個個方超係NPC黎 <br />\n<br />\n台服玩家比人禁言之後就搵其他方法，於是係團隊招募面板（類似係一個組隊平台，入面講呢個組係打副本／刷野／ｅｔｃ）到表達自己既不滿<br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/202004/93a7ccc4f6bb790bf208f25587d51783.JPG?w=1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F202004%2F93a7ccc4f6bb790bf208f25587d51783.JPG%3Fw%3D1000&h=a99b969a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VkD8HRd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVkD8HRd.jpg&h=47e9f73d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g3QvbK0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg3QvbK0.jpg&h=bb4c84e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n亦都有玩家用自己方式表達自己不滿<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G4mm2Rk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG4mm2Rk.jpg&h=26945f91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dLE4gbx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdLE4gbx.jpg&h=e99058ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GSf3wKS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGSf3wKS.jpg&h=2096a1bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>4/5日12點半，中國原廠官方人員鹹魚有話說表示『有可能』中止台服營運。<br />\n資料取至貼吧</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/202004/2926d1b00e4580c34d8760340c437930.JPG?w=1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F202004%2F2926d1b00e4580c34d8760340c437930.JPG%3Fw%3D1000&h=5bb65897&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2020年凌晨4月5日<br />\n黑馬戰光以及遭封鎖玩家解鎖上線/言論封鎖解除/西山居原廠發布聲明</span></span></blockquote><br />\n係<span style=\"color: red;\">黑馬戰光</span>講完句野１２個鐘後<br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/202004/ee682263b10789b5db077be78ab5a094.JPG?w=1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F202004%2Fee682263b10789b5db077be78ab5a094.JPG%3Fw%3D1000&h=0672cdbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原廠西山居放聲明表明勒令台服要整改<br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/202004/cc7460b043bc7d4141b9aac10a439511.JPG?w=1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F202004%2Fcc7460b043bc7d4141b9aac10a439511.JPG%3Fw%3D1000&h=fb687e49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>台服原廠唔跪</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，維護台服玩家言論自由不惜解除合約<br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/202004/2aeec3a9577c506ec96c374e72bca091.JPG?w=1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F202004%2F2aeec3a9577c506ec96c374e72bca091.JPG%3Fw%3D1000&h=20a0591f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n西山居既回應<br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/202004/a5fe44f87d630c61eea9943ffba9089b.JPG?w=1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F202004%2Fa5fe44f87d630c61eea9943ffba9089b.JPG%3Fw%3D1000&h=59541eba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/202004/6e932d3fc536cd8ce5b66862b6f19be6.JPG?w=1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F202004%2F6e932d3fc536cd8ce5b66862b6f19be6.JPG%3Fw%3D1000&h=e9ae7057&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/202004/841515cf138f6837718a8e558e481f29.JPG?w=1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F202004%2F841515cf138f6837718a8e558e481f29.JPG%3Fw%3D1000&h=d0633d44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n豉油：<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=16357&amp;snA=41704&amp;fbclid=IwAR1WepOKJQggO6QXXOPuFUd2c3eNNQpRIp5FEGfvXbFz1LhSn9YFZFC4YFI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D16357%26snA%3D41704%26fbclid%3DIwAR1WepOKJQggO6QXXOPuFUd2c3eNNQpRIp5FEGfvXbFz1LhSn9YFZFC4YFI&d=635WHVioB6XLrmiJ2plDD4kJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=89f4b1f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=16357&amp;snA=41704&amp;fbclid=IwAR1WepOKJQggO6QXXOPuFUd2c3eNNQpRIp5FEGfvXbFz1LhSn9YFZFC4YFI</a><br />\n呢單野亦都比台灣媒體轉載左出去：<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-04-05/386272\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2020-04-05%2F386272&d=635WHVioB6XLrmiJ2plDD4kJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=9773fccd\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-04-05/386272</a>"},{"pid":"d3845c0a208933ba7f241e17aa4b11ace71cae49","tid":1958614,"uid":76234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T19:12:30.000Z","msg":"型"},{"pid":"6d58bfbb32cf8301f57e49be6affb0cf793a91f6","tid":1958614,"uid":162270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T19:16:39.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"f6c858c0219c9ba2bda61dec59412b1e097c126f","tid":1958614,"uid":28013,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T19:17:52.000Z","msg":"總結：唔知大家有無讀過六國論，呢件事正正就係佢既具體化<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>今日割五城，明日割十城，然後得一夕安寢。起視四境，而秦兵又至矣。然則諸侯之地有限，暴秦之慾無厭，奉之彌繁，侵之愈急。故不戰而強弱勝負已判矣。至於顛覆，理固宜然。古人云：&ldquo;以地事秦，猶抱薪救火，薪不盡，火不滅。&rdquo;此言得之。</strong></span></span></blockquote><br />\n可能咁多位巴打會覺得呢個係一個大陸ｇａｍｅ，完全唔關自己事，係玩大陸驚既人自己既事，但事實證明對方只會得寸進尺，就算今日網銀封晒所有發表唔滿意支那既玩家（GIVEN 我地唔理台灣人係自己地方鬧中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) ，西山居下一句咪又係要網銀整頓個聊天頻，要過濾敏感言論